channel.title: Server tracker messed up?
channel.description: Wow, fuck sake. I was up since 4/09/2010 at 100 percent uptime, now I dropped to 99. It says server is currently offline, yet I'm on server with 20 other people as we speak. Checked on Canyouseeme.org and port is open and accepting connections. What's up?
